_:N81ee0a9453da46d798509f62fc6fd931 <http://schema.org/description> "The Committee on Climate Change (CCC) advises the government on emissions targets and reports to Parliament on progress made in reducing greenhouse gas emissions. CCC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero ." .
